<L>__{13. i n t . l e o ' s d a y}
<A>__{a working class bar, an alcoholic or two, pinball machines. schuyler sits a table near a window, checking his watch, it's not his kind of place. a waitress arrives in a too small uniform young, multiple earrings, christine according to her name tag.}
<C>__{christine}
<D>__{can i take your order?}
<C>__{schuyler}
<D>__{i haven't seen the menu.}
