<D>__{you didn't bake me a cake, did you?}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{you can't still be mad about the hash brownies...}
<A>__{schuyler's unamused by the memory. david grins and pulls a small envelope out of his pocket, tosses it on the table in front of him.}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{happy birthday, bro.}
